Module mesakit.data.formats.pbf
Package com.telenav.mesakit.map.data.formats.pbf.model.identifiers

Interface PbfIdentifierType

All Known Implementing Classes:
PbfNodeIdentifier, PbfRelationIdentifier, PbfWayIdentifier
public interface PbfIdentifierType
Implements type encoding for different kinds of PBF identifiers. This class is roughly a "mix-in" through default method implementations and interface fields.
